title: Frank Lloyd Wright 2024 Wall Calendar
description:
The Frank Lloyd Wright 2024 Wall Calendar showcases twelve stunning decorative patterns originally designed by Frank Lloyd Wright himself, presented in vibrant new colors.

This official Frank Lloyd Wright 2024 Wall Calendar is a spiral-bound, interactive calendar that showcases a dynamic selection of iconic stained glass patterns in fresh contemporary colors, patterns originally created by one of the most celebrated architects of the twentieth century. Each month includes a pattern key with the history of each Frank Lloyd Wright design.

  • Dimensions: 14 x 10 in. when displayed
  • Spiral binding for hanging in your home or office
  • 12 monthly grids
  • Sophisticated Frank Lloyd Wright patterns each month
  • Simple date reference
